This repository contains configuration for the JASMIN Scientific Analysis Platform.  Including:

 * RPM SPEC files for building rpms
 * A test suite for verifying the intergrity of the system
 * A system for populating JASMIN wiki pages with the status of supported rpms.

http://www.jasmin.ac.uk/
http://proj.badc.rl.ac.uk/cedaservices/wiki/JASMIN/AnalysisPlatform

Running the Test Suite
======================

The test suite requires NoseXUnitLite to produce reports compatible
with Jenkins.  In order to setup the test environment create a
virtualenv using the system site packages and install the dependencies
into it::

  $ virtualenv --system-site-packages venv
  $ venv/bin/pip install -U NoseXUnitLite nose

